<p><code>x</code> can go to zero even faster in the opposite direction:</p>

<pre><code>int x = 10;

while( 0 &lt;---- x )
{
   printf("%d ", x);
}
</code></pre>

<p><code>8 6 4 2</code></p>

<p>You can control speed with an arrow!</p>

<pre><code>int x = 100;

while( 0 &lt;-------------------- x )
{
   printf("%d ", x);
}
</code></pre>

<p><code>90 80 70 60 50 40 30 20 10</code></p>

<p>;)</p>
